snippet.title: Stray - Official Xbox Release Date Trailer | Annapurna Interactive Showcase 2023
snippet.description:
Lost, alone, and separated from family, a stray cat must untangle an ancient mystery to escape a long-forgotten city.

Stray will be coming to Xbox Series X|S and Xbox One on August 10th.

#IGN
